text: Jesper Thusgård Kristiansen (born 9 December 1966) is a Danish rower. He competed in the men's eight event at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1966 births Category:Living people Category:Danish male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Denmark Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:People from Holstebro Municipality
